# Typography Practice

**Objective:**  
Enhance visual communication through creative typography.

**Tools Used:**  
Canva

**Description:**  
- Created 3 text-based designs experimenting with font pairing, hierarchy, spacing, and alignment.  
- Focused on readability and aesthetic appeal.  
- Explored psychological effects of type styles to create impact.

**Deliverables:**  
- Images: 
  - `Image.1.png`
  - `Image.2.png`
  - `Image.2.png`  
- Source file (Canva): [View Canva Source] https://www.canva.com/design/DAHAj1yZUKI/7jCOhRWsz2KAQKTvY0Vaag/edit?utm_content=DAHAj1yZUKI&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=link2&utm_source=sharebutton 

**Design Logic:**  
- Font Pairing: Used combination of serif and sans-serif fonts.  
- Alignment & Spacing: Carefully adjusted for balance and visual flow.  
- Color & Style: Selected color schemes to evoke emotion and attention.
